# Core engine rules

- `packages/schema` is the contract source. Edit schemas first, export inferred TS types, and parse at boundaries.
- `packages/core` has no LLM/API/model calls. Playwright is only for capture; tests use committed JSON.
- `diagnose.ts` may import `@tell/redesign` only for deterministic measured reconciliation data.
- Detectors are pure: `(fingerprint, capture) => Finding[]`.
- Emit deterministic `facts` and `evidence`; the taste layer judges final verdicts.
- Keep all 14 detectors in `packages/core/src/detectors` unless a real split is needed.
- Detector changes require golden coverage against `fixtures/reports/capture.json`.
- Use `@tell/core-engineer` subagent for new schemas, capture, fingerprint, or detectors.
